### Seller7 Studio — Auth API Manual Tests
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client extension or JetBrains HTTP Client

@base = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@contentType = Content-Type: application/json

### ── HEALTH ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{base}}/health

### ── AUTH ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Signup
# @name signup
POST {{base}}/auth/signup
{{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass1"
}

### 2. Signup — duplicate (expect 409)
POST {{base}}/auth/signup
{{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass1"
}

### 3. Signup — validation failure (expect 422)
POST {{base}}/auth/signup
{{contentType}}

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "password": "weak"
}

### 4. Login
# @name login
POST {{base}}/auth/login
{{contentType}}

{
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass1"
}

### 5. Login — wrong password (expect 401 generic message)
POST {{base}}/auth/login
{{contentType}}

{
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "WrongPassword9"
}

### 6. GET /me — requires Bearer token from login response
# Replace <ACCESS_TOKEN> with the accessToken from step 4
GET {{base}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 7. PATCH /me — update name
PATCH {{base}}/users/me
{{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "name": "Jane Updated"
}

### 8. GET /me — no token (expect 401)
GET {{base}}/users/me

### 9. Refresh tokens (reads refresh cookie automatically in REST Client)
POST {{base}}/auth/refresh

### 10. Forgot password
POST {{base}}/auth/forgot-password
{{contentType}}

{
  "email": "jane@example.com"
}

### 11. Forgot password — non-existent email (same response, no enumeration)
POST {{base}}/auth/forgot-password
{{contentType}}

{
  "email": "nobody@nowhere.com"
}

### 12. Reset password
# Grab the raw token from the console log (DEV) or email link (?token=...)
POST {{base}}/auth/reset-password
{{contentType}}

{
  "token": "<RAW_RESET_TOKEN_FROM_CONSOLE>",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePass2"
}

### 13. Reset password — expired/bad token (expect 400)
POST {{base}}/auth/reset-password
{{contentType}}

{
  "token": "invalid_token_value",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePass2"
}

### 14. Logout — requires Bearer token
POST {{base}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 15. Use old refresh token after logout (expect 401)
POST {{base}}/auth/refresh

### 16. 404 route
GET {{base}}/nonexistent
